snippet.title: PARANORMASIGHT: The Seven Mysteries of Honjo | Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
A new haunting supernatural mystery adventure from Square Enix.
 
Pre-orders are available on Steam® now for 20% off
Pre-orders start on Nintendo Switch™ February 20th for 20% off
How far would you go to bring someone back from the dead?
PARANORMASIGHT launches on Nintendo Switch™ on March 9th and Steam® on March 8th!
